{"tid":15160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實 lihkg已九成取代高登地位","createTime":"2016-12-01T00:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T01:26:49.000Z","uid":44163,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0bae82346590fcfcb89fa2a0a5a67b5c27956b71","tid":15160,"uid":44163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T00:39:12.000Z","msg":"有部分人認為lihkg會步膠登後塵/d人好快走云云<br />\n好明顯佢地冇睇清楚全部既現實<br />\n<br />\n首先<br />\nLihkg有舊hkg+會戶既支持 <br />\n好多用戶都係鍾情hkg+呢個app<br />\n忠誠度十分高<br />\n因此只要lihkg繼續用hkg+既介面做基礎<br />\n就絕對留到呢班用家<br />\n<br />\n其二<br />\nLihkg作為一個多元論壇 <br />\n受惠於hkg+既助力底下已有強大既人流（可以睇隔離數據post)<br />\n更重要既係 大家可以入去任何一個台<br />\n都會見到每個台都有人落地生根<br />\n就比作一個多元生態（每名user)既生態系統咁（lihkg本身）<br />\n所以我睇唔到有咩原因令呢到既用家要去返高登<br />\n<br />\n唯一高登有呢到冇既野就係垃圾管理"},{"pid":"184e2945f6c8e9d56f681b858a43d0f4ed1c86f4","tid":15160,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T00:40:40.000Z","msg":"高登 joe lam<br />\nwho care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日都要理d芝麻綠豆咪好唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c15431c055328acdc1daf077464fc363f2284c0","tid":15160,"uid":29460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T00:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高登 joe lam<br />\nwho care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日都要理d芝麻綠豆咪好唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96aaa33381ac3b1592926abab15d1c80828c34d2","tid":15160,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T00:43:55.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食屎啦林早洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},